energy_sd_model <- brm(
  energy_sd ~ 1 + (1 | participant_id),
  data = df,
  family = gaussian(),
  chains = 4,
  iter = 4000,
  warmup = 1000,
  cores = parallel::detectCores(),
  control = list(adapt_delta = 0.95),
  seed = 123
)
